The paper deals with capacity region of index coding, which is a problem in information theory. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves graph theory and coding theory, which are related to network information (cs.NI) and data structures (cs.DS), respectively. The paper also discusses optimal decoding, which is related to signal processing (cs.SI). Finally, the paper involves polymatroidal single-letter expression, which is related to computational complexity (cs.CC).
